f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kpF0Bl-RAZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkpF0Bl-RAZI&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=7691e9bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kpF0Bl-RAZI</a>"},{"pid":"44812a2b1b688e08483f78cb6dd99f429a9299ed","tid":1568634,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d251753180cb93740c82f3a5df69bbfe9b97b4b","tid":1568634,"uid":125380,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"直接天滅中共啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"開啟新戰線：「天滅中共 平反六四」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正式輸出革命<br />\n<br />\n係大陸人比較多嘅地方，<br />\neg. ifc國歌集會，上水羅湖落馬洲邊境，大學內地生（NDS) 聚腳場合<br />\n<br />\n1）不斷傳播解放軍89六四當年鎮壓市民真相<br />\n<br />\n2）瘋狂播《血染的風采》，播到中共連每日150單程證都唔夠膽放落嚟為止，彭麗媛版本更理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）要將「天滅中共，平反六四」加入為一主要口號，用國語讀更佳<br />\n（如果見到啲廢老藍絲拍片最好叫呢句，啲官媒一定唔夠膽將啲片傳返上大陸，要令佢哋嘅維穩工作白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8&amp;list=RDutvG-uwDsD8&amp;start_radio=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DutvG-uwDsD8%26list%3DRDutvG-uwDsD8%26start_radio%3D1&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=6f0450b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8&amp;list=RDutvG-uwDsD8&amp;start_radio=1</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n也許我告別 將不再回來 你是否理解 你是否明白<br />\n也許我倒下 再不能起來 你是否還要 永久的期待<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n<br />\n也許我的眼睛 再不能睜開 你是否理解 我沉默的情懷<br />\n也許我長眠 將不能醒來 你是否相信 我化作了山脈<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人話：「呢啲係鄰國嘅事，我哋顧掂自己香港，爭取真普選先」<br />\n請你哋block Q咗呢啲人，果啲係五毛嚟<br />\n因為而家係鄰國過去咁多年每日每分每秒搞鳩緊我哋<br />\n<br />\n鄰國愈亂，自顧不暇，各省地方勢力掘起，對我哋有利</span>"},{"pid":"58258c1f28188c3d66c94630e27204a2070adae6","tid":1568634,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cbee3273033379c63e02ff48a8ded3901e2560a","tid":1568634,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"你嗌陳雲果句驅除共黨 光復香港都無咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"李一平有解釋點解拉習近平落馬可以有助中共解體，佢話黨內分裂係最好嘅時機令中共解體。大家可以睇下呢段片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z1sKkNBl_Jc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ1sKkNBl_Jc&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=c2979939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z1sKkNBl_Jc</a>"},{"pid":"9f3b3b2548963cd18aee48381bb940bbaae1c026","tid":1568634,"uid":258113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05c60ab00cfbc26b8fe98784d1d4550746c62ea7","tid":1568634,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"仲有，叫習近平落台可以打屈我地港獨既人幾巴"},{"pid":"2f3c01811dd322e031e9ee5a733322524e8747c5","tid":1568634,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p